{"id": "326a6f5090279267b33d67647400777625c794dc004608b179d13d7ce9c9dd34", "item_id": "8476529cd2:0", "text": "渲染 Fur（皮毛）"}
{"id": "28c1475243adc6747564b5889e454ef8bf35ce0a922d81a54fa29c2c5836959d", "item_id": "8476529cd2:1", "text": "要使用 RenderMan 渲染 Houdini fur（皮毛），需要添加必需的 RenderMan curve attributes（曲线属性），并使用"}
{"id": "ccf31fc48275c143b867da4b33a4ee3f6d4e505c6b15e85616384686e98b23fe", "item_id": "8476529cd2:2", "text": "PxrMarschnerHair"}
{"id": "2086d0f856108844ec3fc72b534b9cf42f04961ace4fd25ddbff21a055e82449", "item_id": "8476529cd2:3", "text": "hair Bxdf（毛发 Bxdf）。"}
{"id": "5c2836cc1089e057004abbc2b9f3c7c50abc67c31601cecbdae2b74260ad014f", "item_id": "8476529cd2:4", "text": "添加 Curves Attributes（曲线属性）"}
{"id": "ab687e11b7f25fc5f9b53ac6c3c0530988e747f371eed329240277b4e5f638fc", "item_id": "8476529cd2:5", "text": "通常只需要添加 width attribute（宽度属性），因为默认宽度相当...粗。"}
{"id": "eb1b712889998e48fd85711a1b3620eec38e014636ab2562f9bec445e9edaa65", "item_id": "8476529cd2:6", "text": "将宽度设置为所需值，并为清晰起见将其命名为 \"width\"。"}
{"id": "8510c9b6e513c05cd865d8eadc2fb285133680a9a975a023520c139d2d6da57c", "item_id": "8476529cd2:7", "text": "对于 cubic（三次）"}
{"id": "7ed7de01e23db500e32e8be0baedd0ac524f756451203e81e2da61c39a05a8ba", "item_id": "8476529cd2:8", "text": "Bezier"}
{"id": "94dae4007b1d8b8d34cc412219083446dbc5754e38f3000c3de5bac6d315f614", "item_id": "8476529cd2:9", "text": "曲线插值，需要将"}
{"id": "6bafedc4ca2d7e479487ff4bdcca30a250a80255867c31100713914d0f24c54a", "item_id": "8476529cd2:10", "text": "Guide Groom"}
{"id": "258f49111ec1571caeface6eb418d1cba58f7cc194b58c473ef9bbc773ae1adf", "item_id": "8476529cd2:11", "text": "节点的"}
{"id": "a452658472fa57996513819e4e72654d203589ad32c7c6343e62882f66577416", "item_id": "8476529cd2:12", "text": "Guide Creation/Segments"}
{"id": "efc14e9de3b95c6110368f36a13d2cf30dc768bfb98cd9a793a3d656a4defdd2", "item_id": "8476529cd2:13", "text": "设置为"}
{"id": "9d486a2eeb1ba1df6659cc6e1ee7f93eadd4436593003e987679f324aa84a2a7", "item_id": "8476529cd2:14", "text": "3 的倍数"}
{"id": "1ef13f95b74b6af58aaa9592f0b7b9ee67a9e214ae4a6a4278729d4a4ebaed2b", "item_id": "8476529cd2:15", "text": "，例如 3、6、9 等。"}
{"id": "c41ce09763ce1b5e608ef35e86badcc54edc24c775e6983735e80d7d81a3c456", "item_id": "8476529cd2:16", "text": "在 ROP 的 Dicing（切分）下，请注意 minimum hair width（最小毛发宽度）控制项，它会以像素为单位全局设置毛发的最小宽度。非常细的毛发在渲染时可能需要更多 minimum samples（最小采样数），以避免 aliasing（走样）或漏渲染毛发。"}
{"id": "a7cfe06af8d841edcbfd738c2bf7c4e1c98bb775d970604a82d28dfda8c9cbdc", "item_id": "8476529cd2:17", "text": "创建并指定 Hair Shader（毛发着色器）"}
{"id": "d4b88dada7e8b0ec80b2bda09067be786a7adcd588fa1ea723ae7e49a101cc70", "item_id": "8476529cd2:18", "text": "进入 fur 的 shopnet。在 fur Network 中创建 PxrMaterialBuilder Network 和 PxrMarschnerHair。"}
{"id": "68cb752a94054d617171d2c027c43c0bcc624d6287a86c2ce445d3d061e37cf6", "item_id": "8476529cd2:19", "text": "将 fur object（皮毛对象）的 Material（材质）设置为指向这个 shader path（着色器路径）。"}
{"id": "83af6264249a28799b0d5af46d0034ed77fe90d4f2c2b812ca7543e77a0d7979", "item_id": "8476529cd2:20", "text": "请注意，默认使用 tube hair（管状毛发）"}
{"id": "c8a69f69754487458ba1b8ff473d119702d7e43925fae45475156780939bc606", "item_id": "8476529cd2:21", "text": "除非"}
{"id": "656bc1af47c6ec08a876a2eefd3c32e06186c3d1954ad25d119ddba4bda8be47", "item_id": "8476529cd2:22", "text": "提供了 normals（法线），这时它们会变成 ribbons（带状曲线）。Camera-facing/billboard curves（面向摄影机/公告板曲线）"}
{"id": "254bb97b57f12e1608fefc4517de768427b2fd6d2cffbbfcbc09f3c818198d5f", "item_id": "8476529cd2:23", "text": "不可用。"}
{"id": "1ec22de1446b40ef378b9d2fcc733cfa91161fe3d1e81ac659f9584b745fcb1d", "item_id": "8476529cd2:24", "text": ""}
{"id": "34e108c0896d0158ca4f2797d4f12a143943803be2151aa5d2136ea1bcd9a468", "item_id": "8476529cd2:25", "text": "显示"}
{"id": "8fb9253aee482c7d793c7d6db8cebea10e8ce9c8781a379d11be9bb415b4fa00", "item_id": "8476529cd2:26", "text": "关闭其他节点的 display（显示），让视图中只显示 fur（皮毛）。"}
{"id": "e736181b0636622113f213d811899c966632e244ce9fb9c1d71cf997216e4d3f", "item_id": "8476529cd2:27", "text": "渲染！"}
